@startuml
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor Admin
participant "Frontend\n(CropManagementDashboard)" as DASH
participant "Frontend\n(CampanaDetail)" as DETAIL
participant "API Service\n(api.js)" as API
participant "Campanas Routes/Controller" as CTRL
database "MySQL\ncampanas, diario, remisiones" as DB
participant "jsPDF" as PDF

== Crear campaña ==
Admin -> DASH: Completa formulario campaña
DASH -> API: crearCampana(payload)
API -> CTRL: POST /campanas (JWT)
CTRL -> DB: INSERT campanas
DB --> CTRL: campana creada
CTRL --> API: 201 { data: campana }
API --> DASH: campana
DASH -> Admin: Actualiza tabla de campañas

== Abrir detalle ==
Admin -> DETAIL: Entrar a /admin/campanas/:id
DETAIL -> API: fetchCampana(id)
API -> CTRL: GET /campanas/:id
CTRL -> DB: SELECT campana
DB --> CTRL: campana
CTRL --> API: 200 { data: campana }

DETAIL -> API: fetchCampanaDiario(id)
API -> CTRL: GET /campanas/:id/diario
CTRL -> DB: SELECT campanas_diario
DB --> CTRL: registros
CTRL --> API: 200 { data: diario }

DETAIL -> API: fetchRemisiones(id)
API -> CTRL: GET /campanas/:id/remisiones
CTRL -> DB: SELECT remisiones
DB --> CTRL: remisiones
CTRL --> API: 200 { data: remisiones }

== Crear o editar remisión ==
Admin -> DETAIL: Guardar remisión
DETAIL -> API: crearRemision(...) / actualizarRemision(...)
API -> CTRL: POST/PUT /campanas/:id/remisiones
CTRL -> DB: INSERT/UPDATE remisiones
DB --> CTRL: remisión persistida
CTRL --> API: 200/201 { data: remision }
API --> DETAIL: remision

== Generar PDF con firmas ==
Admin -> DETAIL: Abrir modal de firma
Admin -> DETAIL: Confirmar "Generar PDF"
DETAIL -> PDF: construir documento (datos + firmas)
PDF --> Admin: remision_campana_{id}_#{remisionId}.pdf
@enduml
